content.html: Really wonder how Matt Damon, Lebron, Spike Lee, Larry David, etc feel or will feel when this is all over. This ain't like selling someone a product. They straight up convinced naive fans of theirs who admire and trust them to be bag holders. How does that not weigh on your soul?
